graph TB
    subgraph "MLflow Operator"
        Controller[MLflow Operator Controller<br/>Go Operator]
        HelmEngine[Embedded Helm Chart<br/>Template Engine]
        HTTPRouteCtrl[HTTPRoute Controller]
        ConsoleLinkCtrl[ConsoleLink Controller]

        Controller -->|renders templates| HelmEngine
        Controller -->|creates| HTTPRouteCtrl
        Controller -->|creates| ConsoleLinkCtrl
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources per MLflow CR"
        MLflowServer[MLflow Server<br/>Python Application<br/>Port: 8443/TCP HTTPS]
        MLflowService[MLflow Service<br/>ClusterIP 8443/TCP]
        MLflowSA[ServiceAccount: mlflow-sa]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>2Gi default]
        HTTPRoute[HTTPRoute<br/>Gateway API]
        ConsoleLink[ConsoleLink<br/>OpenShift Console]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>TCP/8443 ingress]

        MLflowServer -->|exposes| MLflowService
        MLflowServer -->|uses| MLflowSA
        MLflowServer -->|mounts| PVC
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| MLflowCR[MLflow CR<br/>mlflow.opendatahub.io/v1]
    MLflowCR -->|watched by| Controller

    HelmEngine -->|generates| MLflowServer
    HelmEngine -->|generates| MLflowService
    HelmEngine -->|generates| MLflowSA
    HelmEngine -->|generates| PVC

    HTTPRouteCtrl -->|creates| HTTPRoute
    ConsoleLinkCtrl -->|creates| ConsoleLink

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|watches/creates| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    HTTPRoute -->|routes via| Gateway[data-science-gateway<br/>Gateway API]
    ConsoleLink -->|integrates| OSConsole[OpenShift Console]

    %% MLflow Server Dependencies
    MLflowServer -.->|optional| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL Database<br/>5432/TCP TLS]
    MLflowServer -.->|optional| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    MLflowServer -->|auth check| K8sAPI

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| Controller

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HelmEngine fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HTTPRouteCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ConsoleLinkCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MLflowServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MLflowCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Gateway fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PostgreSQL fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
